Title: Hindu Jagrana Vedike activists attack two for transporting cows in Udupi
Content: A Bharatiya Janata Party worker, Praveen Poojary (29), was beaten to death with steel rods allegedly by activists of the Hindu Jagrana Vedike (HJV) for transporting cattle at Karjike in Udupi distric
Author: Ganesh Prabhu
